species.name: tapu-lele
descriptions: Although called a guardian deity, Tapu Lele is devoid of guilt about its cruel disposition and can be described as nature incarnate.
As it flutters about, it scatters its strangely glowing scales. Touching them is said to restore good health on the spot.
It heals the wounds of people and Pokémon by sprinkling them with its sparkling scales. This guardian deity is worshiped on Akala.
This guardian deity of Akala is guilelessly cruel. The fragrant aroma of flowers is the source of its energy.

abilities.name: psychic-surge
abilities.effect: When this Pokémon enters battle, it changes the terrain to Psychic Terrain.

abilities.name: telepathy
abilities.effect: Protects against friendly Pokémon's damaging moves.
